dialogues: Grace: T-That’s my f-friend, Kaitlyn. She’s letting me s-stay here for a while.
Grace: Oh, god. You don’t think she hates me, do you?
Grace: I keep taking advantage of her.
Grace: Having her hide me here from that disgusting man.
Grace: Whilst I have to keep fighting to be able to keep seeing my baby boy.
Grace: Oh lord, please let this end.
Ebenezer: M-Maybe… you should take a little breather.
Grace: Sorry, I didn’t mean to share that much…
